TITLE: Minting into Existing Kiosk using TypeScript and Kiosk SDK
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to mint an item directly into a user's existing kiosk. It includes getting the kiosk owner cap, creating a transaction, and minting an item using a custom contract function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/ts-sdks/blob/main/packages/docs/content/kiosk/kiosk-client/kiosk-transaction/examples.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_0

