TITLE: Adding Objects Created in Transaction
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to add newly created objects to a zkSend link within the same transaction. Shows integration with transaction creation and object reference handling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/ts-sdks/blob/main/packages/docs/content/zksend/link-builder.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const tx = new Transaction();

const link = new ZkSendLinkBuilder({
	sender: '0x...',
});

const newObject = tx.moveCall({
	target: `${PACKAGE_ID}::your_module::mint`,
});

link.addClaimableObjectRef({
	ref: newObject,
	type: `${PACKAGE_ID}::your_module::YourType`,
});

// Adds the link creation transactions to the transaction
link.createSendTransaction({
	transaction: tx,
});
```

